From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 08:12:25 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 04/13] Add callback API and custom launcher
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The shim grew ears — two callback hooks,
So launchers can call without Chromium books.
dlsym six symbols, register, then run,
Zero headers needed. The decoupling's done.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
